---
title: Halloween Haunted Chilli with Spooky Tortilla Chips and Guacamole Goo!
description: There’s nothing like a warm, bubbling chilli on a cold night. In celebration of the spookiest day of the year, round up your little monsters have a go at creating some scary shapes for the pie topping. Finish with a dollop of guacamole goo. You’d be ghoulish not to like this one!
